{"tid":1837377,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國出動機械人治療新型肺炎患者","createTime":"2020-01-23T15:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T02:02:51.000Z","uid":37554,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"66423ca2d1b3a7f6789977981ed6e9700cacd926","tid":1837377,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】美國首宗新型冠狀病毒患者康復進度良好，當地使用應付伊波拉病毒的特殊病房，又出動機械人隔離治療患者。<br />\n確診的30多歲男患者，在華盛頓州埃弗里特市一間醫院留醫。醫院傳染病部門主管說，院方是用隔離艙將他從家中帶到醫院，直接送入「特殊病原體」病房。<br />\n<br />\n這種特殊病房2015年為應對伊波拉疫情爆發時設立，今次是首次使用。面積6米乘6米，只有一個出入口，由保安看守。患者只能在房內活動。<br />\n為了盡量減少直接接觸，病房安裝了機械人，配備聽筒等基本醫療設備。醫生在房外操作機械人為患者診治。<br />\n<br />\n院方安排四名接受過特別訓練的護士專責照顧患者，連同其他醫護人員，總共只有十多人獲准接近。院方說他康復進度良好，但未提及何時可離開隔離病房。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/211606263207381/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F211606263207381%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeGztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=40c2608a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/211606263207381/</a>"},{"pid":"930674f8ed49cf1cd6d3ee1b9e1211c9bdf5d246","tid":1837377,"uid":191812,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"高下立見"},{"pid":"faa06cb12e45c523ef68dc4d7f2d60081d879002","tid":1837377,"uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87303f475d3a5f2828608490deb29effb0384568","tid":1837377,"uid":194298,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"免費白老鼠，問武漢拎多兩隻"},{"pid":"636ed7987d4b6a0f18b63d1882f8ff1d7539389d","tid":1837377,"uid":152241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:17:40.000Z","msg":